<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٧١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3">آدَمُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1580">الْحَكَمُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/128">إِبْرَاهِيمَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/710">الْأَسْوَدِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a>قَالَتْ: <span class="c2">«كَأَنِّي أَنْظُرُ إِلَى وَبِيصِ الطِّيبِ فِي مَفْرِقِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
